title: DDFP 341: Veteran QBs & Super Bowl rewind
itunes:title: DDFP 341: Veteran QBs & Super Bowl rewind
description:
Shek is joined by Handsome Hank and Gregg Rosenthal from "Around the NFL" to discuss the upcoming seasons of veteran quarterbacks like Philip Rivers, Peyton Manning and more. Shek and Gregg then imagine how the offseason could be different if the Seahawks won the Super Bowl. The guys also update #DDFP bracketology of the greatest movies producer Black Tie has never seen.
